data.description:
Close to Ft Huachuca main gate, this house is perfect for you to put your own touch on it. The bedrooms are very generous in size with tile throughout the
home. In addition to the living room, there is a room off the kitchen and dining room big enough for a pool table. There is a separate laundry room with
storage leading out to the fenced in back yard. The Best is Yet To Come when you come home here!
